	<h1 class="title">《福布斯》公布足球俱乐部价值排行榜，皇马又赢了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/101857/small/101857.jpg?1429073860" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">谢舒敏</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-08 10:30:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/9309/medium/9309.jpg?1436686797" alt="" />			
	</div>
